title: NDS Snood 2 on vacation (E) - P0w3rp0t1
description:
Special Features
 
Four different single player modes to keep the gamer entertained for hours 
Five different difficulty modes always providing a challenge 
Fifty puzzles and fifty Time Attack levels providing diverse game play


Review
 
Downloaded over four million times, one of the biggest Shareware games of all times is back with a vengeance.
More that just a puzzle game, Snood is an engrossing experience. The object is to free the Snoods using the Snood-O-Matic cannon. Join similar Snoods to set them free and watch them drop to safety. But don&#039;t take too long because every Snood launched increases the danger level.
